			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I ran fairly extensive testing on pet HP today, letting mobs take down the pets to 10-20% then having CH land. I got these results:
<br />

<br />
SoAS 65 earth: 6210 average over 13 CH's
<br />
GoDS 65 earth: 5490 average over 9 CH's
<br />
Unfocused 65 earth: 4780 average over 6 CH's
<br />
SoAS 61 air: 4910 average over 11 CH's
<br />
Unfocused 61 air: 3770 average over 11 CH's
<br />

<br />
With very great precision, I can say that GoDS adds 15% HP and SoAS 30%. I'm planning to run tanking tests as well since I've got excellent opportunities to do it.<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=597626">Enharjaren Fenrirsbane</a> 
<br />
Arch Overseers
<br />
Bristlebane
<br />

<br />
